bug.short_desc: Menu not closed when scrolled with mousewheel

long_desc.thetext:
When you scroll with the mousewheel the menus in toolbar / splitbutton are not closed.
How to reproduce? Toolbar / Menu -> click on "Toolbar MenuButton" button -> scroll with mousewheel -> menu is not closed.
Expected behavior? When you scroll by scrollbar or resize the window the menu is closed. I would expecte the same behavior when scrolling by mousewheel.
http://demo.qooxdoo.org/devel/widgetbrowser/

Added a mouse wheel handler to the menu manager to close all open menus on scroll.
